::Prowl::

Prowl nods, his mind working over the places where he could get liquid 
energon. He didn't really know if there was any in the CR room, but... The 
mess hall! There was a replicator there, maybe he could get some liquid 
energon from it!

"I'll be right back!" he spins around, running off toward the mess hall.
